@startuml Customer_Login
title Customer Login Flow (Store-Specific Page)

actor "Customer" as User
participant "Store Login Page\n(store.flowmerce.com/login)" as UI
participant "Auth Service" as Auth
participant "User DB" as DB
participant "Email Service" as Email
participant "Frontend" as FE

User -> UI : Enter email + password
UI -> Auth : POST /auth/customer/login\n{email, password}
Auth -> DB : Find customer by email\n& verify password
DB --> Auth : Return customer record

alt Invalid credentials
    Auth --> UI : 401 Unauthorized\n"Invalid email or password"
    UI --> User : Show error message

else Valid credentials
    Auth -> DB : Check email_verified flag
    DB --> Auth : Return verified status

    alt Email not verified
        Auth -> Email : Resend verification email
        Auth --> UI : 403 Forbidden\n"Please verify your email"
        UI --> User : Show verify email prompt

    else Email verified
        Auth -> DB : Generate refresh token\n& store it
        Auth --> UI : 200 OK\n{accessToken, refreshToken}

        UI -> FE : Store tokens
        FE --> User : Redirect to Store Homepage
    end
end

== Token Refresh (background) ==
FE -> Auth : POST /auth/customer/refresh\n{refreshToken}
Auth -> DB : Validate refresh token
Auth --> FE : New accessToken

@enduml
